A simple discord bot for Ars Magic Die rolls
============================================

GPL-3 licensed - see the license file

Commands
---------

/simple [+modifier]
/i [+modifier]

A simple die roll, with optional modifier which is added to the result


/stressed [+modifier]
/ess [+modifier]

A stressed die roll with an optional modifier
Rolls of zero will display 'possible botch' in addition to the total if the roll does not
botch

/botch [number]
/b [number]

Roll *number* botch die (defaulting to 1 if no value given) and report the number of botches

/formulaic [+casting score] [target]
/form [+casting score] [target]

Roll a formulaic spell using a stress die, given the success levels if given
the casting score and target number If just given the casting score, works the
same as a stressed die

/spont [+casting score] [target]
/sp [+casting score] [target]

Roll a non-fatiguing spontaneous spell.

/fspont [+casting scroe] [target]
/fsp [+casting score] [target]

Roll a fatiguing spontaenous spell

Requirements
============

Python 3
discord-py


